### First run — no watermark, RestAdapter fetches every page.
POST http://localhost:4102/pipeline/execute
Content-Type: application/json

{"name":"ExchangeRates","mode":"delta","trigger":"manual"}

### Query the local replica.
GET http://localhost:4102/odata/v4/example/ExchangeRates?$orderby=rateDate desc&$top=10

### Second run — adapter issues `modifiedSince=<tracker.lastSync>` and
### fetches only newer rows. No rows changed upstream → 0 inserts / updates.
POST http://localhost:4102/pipeline/execute
Content-Type: application/json

{"name":"ExchangeRates","mode":"delta","trigger":"manual"}

### Full refresh — clears the local table and replays every page.
POST http://localhost:4102/pipeline/execute
Content-Type: application/json

{"name":"ExchangeRates","mode":"full","trigger":"manual"}

### Filtered analytics on the local replica (no remote hit)
GET http://localhost:4102/odata/v4/example/ExchangeRates?$filter=quoteCurrency eq 'USD'&$orderby=rateDate desc
